HEADWORD: Bicentenary
<hw>Bi*cen"te*na*ry</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>bi-</ets> + <ets>centenary</ets>.]</ety> <def>Of or pertaining to
two hundred, esp. to two hundred years; <as>as, a <ex>bicentenary</ex>
celebration</as>.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>The two hundredth
anniversary, or its celebration.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bicentennial</ent>⟦br⟧
